data.description: Booking your showing now for this Vista Heights-Sparks home with open floorplan, formal and casual dining spaces, perfect for entertaining! Lots of windows for natural light, making the home welcoming and inviting. Spacious kitchen offers ample storage space (including a cabinet pantry), island, and peninsula breakfast bar. 2nd floor loft makes for a great second entertainment space or office. With a little TLC this home will be a forever home to its next owner. Towering trees make the backyard more private and enjoyable, creating an ideal space to relax with friends or enjoy a summer BBQ!  Brand new A/C installed spring of 2020 (with smart thermostat) and ceiling fans throughout the home help circulate the air and keep you comfortable year round. Upstairs you will find three spacious bedrooms plus a loft that is ideal for a movie room, office, home gym or play area. The master bedroom features a window seat that overlooks the beautiful backyard and offers additional storage for bedding and accessories. The master bathroom includes a large vanity with dual sinks, walk-in closet, separate shower stall and a jetted tub, perfect for a hot soak after a long day. Three car garage offers plenty of space for vehicles and recreational equipment. Great neighborhood that feels secluded but is just minutes to shopping and dining and offers easy access to the freeway and major roadways. Zoned for desirable schools including Beasley elementary, the new Sky Ranch middle school and Reed high school.
